trans-unit.source: Enumerates the contents of a binary tree.

**NuGet package**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">about immutable collections and how to install</see>)

This structure should be kept synchronized with the other two binary tree enumerators: <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableList%601.Enumerator?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableSortedDictionary%602.Enumerator?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: 此結構應該保持同步與其他兩個的二進位樹狀目錄列舉值：<xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableList%601.Enumerator?displayProperty=nameWithType>和<xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableSortedDictionary%602.Enumerator?displayProperty=nameWithType>。

trans-unit.source: When this enumerator is used as a value type (that is, when it isn't boxed), do not copy it by assigning it to a second variable or by passing it to another method.
trans-unit.target: 當這個列舉值做為值類型 （亦即，它不會進行 boxed 處理） 時，請勿複製它指派給第二個變數，或將它傳遞給另一種方法。

trans-unit.source: When this enumerator is disposed of, it returns a mutable reference type stack to a resource pool, and if the value type enumerator is copied (which can easily happen unintentionally if you pass the value around), there is a risk that a stack that has already been returned to the resource pool may still be in use by one of the enumerator copies, leading to data corruption or exceptions.
trans-unit.target: 當這個列舉值，會處置時，它會傳回可變動參考類型堆疊至資源集區中，而如果值的類型列舉值複製 （這可以輕鬆地會不小心如果您傳遞周圍值），則會有風險，已經過的堆疊傳回資源集區仍然可能在使用其中一個列舉值的複本，導致資料損毀或例外狀況。
此型別具備執行緒安全。

trans-unit.source: Gets the element at the current position of the enumerator.

**NuGet package**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">about immutable collections and how to install</see>)
The element at the current position of the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 位於目前列舉程式位置的項目。

trans-unit.source: Releases the resources used by the current instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableSortedSet`1.Enumerator" /> class.

**NuGet package**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">about immutable collections and how to install</see>)
Advances the enumerator to the next element of the immutable sorted set.

**NuGet package**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">about immutable collections and how to install</see>)
<see langword="true" /> if the enumerator was successfully advanced to the next element; <see langword="false" /> if the enumerator has passed the end of the sorted set.
Sets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first element in the immutable sorted set.

**NuGet package**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">about immutable collections and how to install</see>)
